    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Featuring your little one’s favorite characters, kids will love to watch their saving grow in this special metal tin coin holder! A fun item to include in your little one’s bedroom that they can use to save coins or keep other treasured belongings safe, the piggy bank is also a great learning tool to impart your little ones the importance of money management, savings, allowance, counting, math and more in a new, fun and engaging way with his or her favorites.</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">Licensed Kids Coin Tin Piggy Bank Learning Savings Tools for Kids (Many Styles)</h2>\n  <p>Featuring your little one’s favorite characters, kids will love to watch their saving grow in this special metal tin coin holder! A fun item to include in your little one’s bedroom that they can use to save coins or keep other treasured belongings safe, the piggy bank is also a great learning tool to impart your little ones the importance of money management, savings, allowance, counting, math and more in a new, fun and engaging way with his or her favorites.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>OFFICIALLY LICENSED DESIGN:</strong> Featuring your little one’s favorite character, kids will love to watch their saving grow in this special metal tin coin holder; a fun item to include in your little one’s bedroom that they can use to save coins or keep other treasured belongings safe</li>\n    <li><strong>FUN KIDS LEARNING TOOL:</strong> Gifting young children, a toddler or kids this metal tin coin collector money bank will make learning about money and savings fun; an excellent learning tool to instill the importance of saving from a young age; the piggy bank is also a great way for kids to practice counting and math at home in a new and fun way</li>\n    <li><strong>DURABLE MATERIAL:</strong> Made from durable, sturdy metal, this piggy bank will stand up to lots of wear and tear as your kids move it throughout the house or use it for pretend play or role play games with friends and family; the tin piggy banks can also be turned into other everyday household items like a pencil holder, wrapped candy stash or girls makeup jar</li>\n    <li><strong>EASILY REMOVEABLE LID:</strong> The piggy banks have a wide slot on the top lip that kids can easily fit coins through or folded dollar bills too; the lid on the top can be easily popped off to retrieve coins and bills, encouraging little ones to keep track of their savings</li>\n    <li><strong>ASSORTED STYLES:</strong> Three different designs featuring your favorite characters. Ships at Random</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1600x1600/25108_green_main.jpg/bank_parent.jpg\" alt=\"Featuring your little one’s favorite characters, kids will love to watch their saving grow in this special metal tin coin holder\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
